text: Hell in a Cell (2014) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view and livestreaming show made by WWE. It took place on October 26, 2014 at American Airlines Center in Dallas, Texas. It was the sixth Hell in a Cell event held by WWE and the first to also stream live on the WWE Network. There were two main events on the card. The first main event saw John Cena defeat Randy Orton to earn a future WWE World Heavyweight Championship match.
